data.description: This exquisite 3-bed, 2-bath home offers a perfect blend of contemporary design & rustic charm - step inside and be greeted by an open-concept layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, & kitchen areas - the polished concrete floors not only exude an air of modern elegance but also provide easy maintenance & durability - natural light pours in through large windows, creating a warm & inviting ambiance that fills every corner of the space - the kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, sleek countertops, & ample cabinet space for all your culinary needs - whether you're whipping up a quick weekday meal or hosting a lavish dinner party, this kitchen provides the perfect backdrop for your culinary adventures - separate dedicated office space - outside, the enchanting back patio beckons you to unwind & indulge in outdoor living at its finest with the stone fireplace serving as an artistic masterpiece - don't miss the chance to make this haven your own!!
